article_title: Our view: Maybe North Jersey casinos aren't inevitable

og.description: Area residents got some holiday cheer this week from an unlikely place: the state Legislature. Political leaders failed to get a vote on a constitutional amendment ending Atlantic City's statewide casino gambling monopoly.
